  <div class="article"> 
   <div class="header"> 
    <div class="title">
     赌王何鸿鲇懈龉侄子：刚赢了200亿的赌局，他就跑去“唱红歌”
    </div> 
    <div> 
     <div class="media">
      ABC企业家俱乐部
     </div> 
     <div class="time">
      2015年08月24日 08:00
     </div> 
    </div> 
   </div> 
   <div class="content "> 
    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-w="480" data-ratio="0.11458333333333333" data-s="300,640" src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/0.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%;"><img data-w="30" data-ratio="0.3333333333333333" data-type="gif" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/1.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%;">点击上方</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 澳中企业家俱乐部</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，一键关注，即刻与澳中企业家高端互动！</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 240); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 4px 4px 2px; background-color: rgb(0, 112, 192); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一个跨澳中的高端商务俱乐部</span></strong></span></p>
    <fieldset class="comment_quote" style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 5px; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 5px 5px 2px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 240); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset class="comment_quote" style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px; min-width: 0px; font-size: 12px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">澳中企业家俱乐部，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">原名ABC</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">企业家俱乐部是</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); max-width: 100%;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">经认证的高端商务俱乐部</span></strong></span>，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); font-family: Arial; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> </span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2007</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">年成立。</span>立足于悉尼，放眼中澳。目前有普通会员超过一千位，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;">VIP及机构</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;">会员一百多位，于2015年2月28日正式更名为澳中企业家俱乐部。</span></span></p>
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); max-width: 100%;">在这里，您可以了解到：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); text-align: justify; max-width: 100%;">澳洲移民、房地产、投资、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">休闲娱乐等信息。</span></span></span></p>
     </fieldset>
    </fieldset>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/2.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">本文转自塔木德富豪会，作者：陈光。</span><br /></p>
    <section data-id="5" data-color="rgb(198, 198, 199)" data-custom="rgb(198, 198, 199)" style="">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">【前言】</span></strong></p>
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何鸿17个子女中，何猷龙被认为最像父亲――五官、才干以及魄力。按照流行界定，暖男、拼爹、刷脸、总裁……他似乎没有死角。</span></p>
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在澳门博彩的寒冬中，这个刚赢得200亿“赌局”，便跑去政协会议上认真做笔记的年轻人，能否续写赌王传奇？</span></p>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" data-color="rgb(172, 29, 16)" data-custom="rgb(172, 29, 16)" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">赌王之子</span></strong></p>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何猷龙，38岁，新濠博亚联席主席，身家34亿美元，2014年位列香港富豪榜第12位，旗下有3家上市公司，手握澳门六块“赌牌”之一。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">然而，如若加上他那条最重要的标签――何鸿龅亩子，这些成绩带来的厚重荣誉感，在普通大众的传统思维里，将成色大减。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这是巨富二代的“普遍待遇”。父辈的成就太高，光环将他们裹得严严实实。置身其中，干得好，是理所当然；干得不好，是纨绔无能。至于个人能力？那并不是舆论关注的重点。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何猷龙头顶的光环，比其他人更大。他的父亲何鸿觯是澳门近现代史上权势最大、获利最多、最具传奇色彩的人。论对澳门的影响力，半个世纪以来，无人能出其右。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/3.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">青年时代的何鸿</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在大众看来：作为赌王的儿子，创下34亿美元的身家很难吗？何猷龙的体会是，光是做“赌王的儿子”，都有点难。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">4、5岁刚记事，“二世祖”的称谓便每天萦绕在他耳边，这是他最熟的词，陪伴其多年。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何鸿鋈⒘怂姆浚生了17个子女。如你所想，“宫斗”在所难免。从1981年大房长子何猷光意外逝世，到1991年三房添下幼子，10年间，何猷龙是何家子嗣中唯一的男丁，承受了最多的“冲击”。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“唯一”并没有给他带来厚爱。何家四房分住，何猷龙和父亲聚少离多。9岁之后，他随母亲移居加拿大，父子见面的次数更是屈指可数。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何猷龙在北美生活了14年，他回忆称那是一段很不愉快的时光。作为黄皮肤的中国人，他在国外“遭排斥，被从小踩到大”。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">期间，他喜欢上了激烈对抗的运动，包括冰球、泰拳。他的理想是成为一名笼斗士：在血腥暴力的笼子里，将轻视他的人打垮在地。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">顶着“赌王之子”的头衔，面对一座翻不过去的大山，何猷龙亟需宣泄与自证。即便后来因工作放弃理想，他仍保留了格斗这个爱好，每周至少打一次泰拳。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他将格斗多年练出的一身肌肉，隐藏在宽松的西服之下。外人不知道，这个一向以温和笑容示人的年轻人，心中的火有多炽热。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">藏着6亿去打工</span></strong></p>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">23岁，大学毕业那年，何猷龙回到香港，他没有进入家族企业，而是拿着简历出去找工作。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">接连面试了十几个企业和部门后，何猷龙到怡富证券做起了最普通的打工仔。他比普通人还拼，是个“加班狂人”。7个月后，他便升任经理助理。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">周围的同事并不知道，这个每天最晚打卡下班、见谁都“低头哈腰”的俊俏后生，刚刚从他爸那里分得6亿港币的资产。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/4.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <br />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何猷龙在外面历练了1年，他称这是为了积累经验，而不是狂妄到和自己的身份与家世对立。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">随后，他褪下了面纱。2000年，何猷龙用从父亲那里得到的资金参股“亚洲网上交易系统有限公司”，将这家企业推上了香港创业板后，他又收购了3家科技公司。2001年互联网泡沫破裂时，他的企业仍旧维持着400万港币的年净利。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">期间，他赢得了“公司医生”的称谓，意指他特别擅长处理那些“破烂”企业，能将收购来的公司焕然一新。2001年，何鸿龈了他一个更大的“病人”：主要业务在香港的新濠国际。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">赌王名下逾百家企业中，新濠国际处在最差的一档。何猷龙接手时，手下就8名员工，已经连续亏损了7年，值得一提的产业只有做餐饮的“珍宝海鲜舫”。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">当时，外界对此有两种解读：一是赌王不看好何猷龙，给他一块“鸡肋”；另外则分析称这是对继承者的“试炼”。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不论出于什么目的，当时的何鸿隹峙乱参戳系剑新濠会在数年的时间内，变身成为与他的“澳博”分庭抗礼的澳门新贵。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“抢”到新座位</span></strong></p>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何猷龙在一年内改变了几乎是“空壳”的新濠。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">期间，他研究了香港百年经济档案，尝了几百道菜，把海鲜坊更名为“珍宝王国”。第一年，“珍宝王国”的销售额涨了37%，此后数年，净利一直维持40%左右的增幅。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/5.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">珍宝王国</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">餐饮显然无法满足他的野望。搞定博彩这台“永动的印钞机”，才是其作为“赌王之子”的使命。将新濠变为“优质壳”后，他希望借此杀回澳门。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何猷龙决定回澳门时，澳门正“战火纷飞”。2002年澳门博彩改制，世界著名的博彩集团蜂拥而至，争夺3张赌牌。最终，何鸿觥⑹返俜-永利各执一张，吕志和联手谢尔登-阿德尔森拿下另一张。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不久后，吕志和与阿德尔森产生争执，赌牌又“3变6”，米高梅伺机进入。大佬们一边打官司，一边建赌场，澳门半岛上的赌城很快超过20家，金沙和银河还跑去胱械嚎火。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">澳门“很挤”，站在角落无人在意的何猷龙，却看到了做成大买卖的机会。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">澳门的赌场分“上中下”三档：贵宾厅、中场业务、老虎机（slot machine）。那时候，本土和外来势力都选择延续澳门赌业的传统，将重心放在贵宾厅上。因为背靠内地，巨贾众多，奢豪、畸形的巨赌，是赌场盈利的大头。贵宾厅占澳门赌场利润的比例，一度超过70%。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">拉斯维加斯的情况恰恰相反，投注额低、娱乐化的老虎机，占据七成的份额。澳门赌场不重视老虎机，因为添设100台老虎机，提供的利润也比不上照顾好一位富商。2003年，全澳老虎机一共800台，而在拉斯维加斯，随便一家赌场都有几千台老虎机。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/6.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">老虎机</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作为闯入者，何猷龙有着不一样的视角。一来，他没有争夺大客户的实力；二来，他觉得，中产阶级同样有消费潜力，并且比重会逐年攀升。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">于是，2003年，他设计了一款新式的老虎机，取名“摩卡”，随即开设了第一家摩卡俱乐部。他把老虎机和自动售货机结合，放到了澳门的各个角落，让游客随时随地“赌上一把”。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“摩卡”很快风靡，比何猷龙预想得还要火。这一年，新濠国际的净利润涨了770%，摩卡俱乐部从1家变成了8家。在其带动下，澳门老虎机的数量翻了数倍，何猷龙硬生生闯开了一条道。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在澳门的赌桌上，他有了自己的座位。周遭的大佬们，开始认得这张27岁的年轻面孔。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">4</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">200亿的“豪赌”</strong></span></p>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">初战告捷，何猷龙决定一鼓作气，再上层楼。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2004年，他联合澳大利亚首富、博彩大亨克里-帕克的儿子詹姆斯-帕克，成立了新濠博亚，出任联席主席兼CEO。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这似是两个富二代追求自我实现的证明，随后，两人将证明变成了豪赌。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2006年初，新濠博亚以9亿美元的天价，从史蒂夫-永利处购得了澳门第六张、也是最后一张赌牌。同年4月，集团宣布将投资200亿人民币，兴建亚洲最大的休闲综合体新濠天地。12月，新濠博亚赴纳斯达克上市，融资超20亿美元，创造了纳市史上最大的博彩IPO。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一场豪赌，何猷龙来到了风暴的中心，各式评论不绝于耳。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">支持来自父亲，何鸿龃侨チ诵洛┕际董事局主席职务，由何猷龙接任。压力则来自各个层面。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“70多亿（澳门元）买赌牌，人家觉得我疯了。”何猷龙说。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不仅质疑他“步子大了，容易扯着”，还有言论称何猷龙对于新濠天地的规划存在根本性错误。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一方面，他花20多亿人民币，为项目打造了全球最大的水上表演《水舞间》。另一方面，赌场只占新濠天地5%的面积，远低于酒店和文化娱乐设施。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/7.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">《水舞间》</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">董事局会议上，有大股东丢给何猷龙两个问题。一，《水舞间》什么时候能回本？二，为什么别的赌场，博彩设施的面积都是50%以上？</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">很少有人能理解他。“因为在新濠天地之前，澳门就是一个博彩的地方，唯一成功的市场就是博彩，没有其他娱乐。”他说。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">剩下的95%，何猷龙拿来做了什么？</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他在新濠天地开了3家酒店，包括皇冠度假酒店、HARD ROCK酒店，以及澳门君悦酒店。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他花3亿人民币，用29000枚剧院式LED灯，建了一个全球最大的圆顶形综合剧院。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他打造了澳门最大的夜店：占地两层、逾3000平米的“娇比”（Club CUBIC），仅装修费用，就花了超过1个亿。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他“铺”了一条新濠大道，卖奢侈品、珠宝和名表；给孩子造了一个“童梦天地”游乐场，还开了个虚拟的水族馆。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/8.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">新濠大道一景</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这些布局的核心，是加大非博彩业务，推动综合性旅游度假休闲娱乐。“每家赌场都一样，就是一张张的赌桌。”何猷龙说：“从长远看，多元化、独特的娱乐体验，才是制胜之道。”</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为了坚持这个理念，他险些赔本离场。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">5</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何家的荣耀</strong></span></p>
     </section>
     <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2008年，金融危机肆虐，寒流直冲博彩行业，不少荷官被“强行”休假，报道称赌王何鸿龅纳砑宜跛了90%。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">资本选择逃离澳门。新濠天地对面，金沙投资的“金光大道”已经停工，新濠天地的新一轮融资方案也步履维艰，有投资者甚至提出撤资。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">项目仍在继续，何猷龙面临巨大的压力。那段时间，他经常出现在工地，很少在舆论面前露面。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/9.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.40794979079497906" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">新濠天地</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2009年6月1日，顶着金融危机的余温，新濠天地开幕。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">开幕庆典上，一向沉稳示人的何猷龙有点放浪形骸，他喝了不少香槟，砸了一把电吉他，还放话说：“四五岁起，就有人说我是纨绔子弟，现在这些人都可以闭嘴了！”</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">你可以理解他的反常。到目前为止，这是他人生中最重要的一个项目。成了，他便是澳门一极，输了，能否卷土重来不好说，纨绔的帽子是戴定了。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如今看来，这个改变何猷龙的项目，也在某些层面改变了澳门。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">09年下半年，澳门博彩复苏，来访群体也悄然变化。胱械旱拿夥寻喑瞪希不再坐满微醺的赌客，有很多家长带着孩子来过周末，新濠的“童梦天地”和虚拟水族馆内，总是很热闹。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/10.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">虚拟水族馆内表演</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">那个曾被股东“骂惨了”的《水舞间》，迄今已经卖出320万张门票，是新濠乃至澳门的王牌项目。新濠甚至有底气称：没看过《水舞间》，就不算来过澳门。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何猷龙的3家酒店，以君悦为例，800间客房全年的入住率约为102%，也就是说，想要入住，就得提前预订。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">过去，澳门的其他娱乐依附于博彩，并不显眼。新濠天地则证明了，力的作用是相互的。2009年底，新濠博亚在澳门博彩业的市场份额由9%上升至18%，涨了一倍。数据面前，曾经荒谬的规划成了正解。重视中产阶级、普通客人的新濠博亚，强势崛起。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">对于家族而言，何猷龙的成功有着更多意义。澳门六张赌牌，他一张，父亲何鸿鲆徽牛姐姐何超琼一张。这意味着，在澳门博彩改制、国际巨头卷动风云的10年之后，何家，依旧把持着行业一半的命脉。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">6</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">澳门“风云”</strong></span></p>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="">可惜“甜蜜期”并不长。何家还是澳门的何家，但澳门不再是曾经的澳门。</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2014年下半年起，澳门“很受伤”。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">官方数据显示，2014年12月，澳门博彩收入暴跌创纪录的30.5％，今年5月份，下降数字来到了37.1%，这是澳门博彩收入连续第12个月下跌。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/11.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">反腐风潮中，澳门赌业受到了冲击</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">风暴中，赌业大亨们的身家纷纷跳水。2014年风光无限，一度被指身家超过李嘉诚的澳门银河娱乐主席吕志和，在2015年香港富豪榜上，从去年的第2位跌至第5，资产大减76亿美元。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">真正让行业恐慌的，不是数字，而是萧条的景象。曾经人声鼎沸的赌场内，出现了不小的“留白”。今年上半年，澳门关闭的贵宾厅已经达到两位数。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这一次和2008年不一样，因为风暴的源头是北京。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">按照澳门业内说法，内地客人贡献的收入超过八成，一掷千万乃至过亿的巨赌，是赌场利润的主要来源。2014年刮起的反腐风潮，让内地“问题”赌客望而却步。一些赌场的VIP，已经成了阶下囚。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">更重要的是，中央政府希望澳门转型。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/12.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
     <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2014年12月20日，习近平主席在澳门回归祖国15周年的讲话中，明确指出要“加强和完善对博彩业的监管，积极培育新的经济增长点，不断推动经济适度多元可持续发展，取得实质性成果。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这次讲话的重要性不言而喻，全澳的人都明白，单一依靠博彩业换取繁华的时代，正在终结。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">7</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“唱红歌”的继承者</span></strong></p>
     </section>
     <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">身处历史拐点，何猷龙的心情有点复杂。一方面，2014年，新濠博亚的纯利下滑至14.87亿港币，比前年少了7个百分点，这是公司成立后首度年营收下滑，他的个人身价也缩水14亿美元。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">另一方面，论博彩“多元化、培育新的经济增长点”，他比其他竞争对手跑得都早――这或许是他一改低调，大胆“发声”的倚仗。在全澳转身的浪潮中，他试图让自己更“显眼”。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">去年12月19日，何猷龙买了整版广告，用大红色的标语欢迎习近平去澳门――“习主席――您好！热烈欢迎习近平主席出席澳门回归十五周年庆典！”</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/13.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
     <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">这则广告挺轰动，网评说这个“上道”的年轻人有点“萌萌哒”。</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">之所以受关注，因为港商继承人里，努力接近政治的年轻人很少，不擅长和政府打交道，被认为是该群体的通性。去年起，李嘉诚开始大量抛售内地资产，当时，一位熟悉他的人向华商名人堂解读说：原因之一是李家面临接班，新一代可能无法像父辈那样处理好政商关系。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作为该群体的一员，何猷龙有点另类。2013年起，他就经常登上内地省台的《新闻联播》。画面里，他端坐于省级的会议厅，播音员字正腔圆地念到：“双方本着互惠互利的原则，增进友谊，加深了解……”身着宽松西服、戴着眼镜的何猷龙，坐在省部级官员身边，居然毫无违和感。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他说：“希望可以运用娱乐方面的经验，到内地发展。”为此，他聘请了一位私人普通话老师，随时学习。在他看来，从小在加拿大长大，因此说不好普通话，是自己很大的缺陷。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他的普通话进步很大。2015年1月12日，在新项目新濠影汇的发布会上，何猷龙用普通话做了致辞，短短几分钟内，他三次提到了“感谢澳门和中央政府”。那种感觉，仿佛下一秒他就会唱起红歌。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“澳门的游客很多是内地同胞，没有中央政府和澳门政府的政策支持，没有自由行的开放，澳门的经济不可能这么成功，所以我真心感谢政府。”何猷龙说。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/14.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">新濠影汇概念图</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">致辞很“官方”，但看他努力咬准音、试图说好普通话的神态，感觉又有点真诚。另一方面，致辞也不需要太具煽动性，因为新濠影汇的图片，已足够吸引与会者的眼球。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">8</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">再赌32亿美元</strong></span></p>
     </section>
     <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p><span style=""><br /></span></p>
    <p><span style="">这是何猷龙打出的新牌。</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他称投资32亿美元的新濠影汇，会给亚洲观众带来最震撼、最顶尖的世界级度假体验。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这座新“City of Dreams”建筑群的正中，将建成高130米的“影汇之星”，这是亚洲最高的摩天轮。建筑群内部，则充斥着以好莱坞电影为主题的，诸多令人神驰的声影奇观。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/15.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">“影汇之星”将成为亚洲最高的摩天轮</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“我们建立了首个蝙蝠侠电影专利的数码动感游戏，也有专为小朋友设计的家庭冒险乐园，酒店平台还将建成人工森林河流带。”何猷龙说。他再一次强调项目的侧重点在休闲旅游，而非纯粹的博彩。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但在被追问两者于利润的贡献时，他又大方承认：非博彩只占小部分，博彩事业仍是新濠博亚营收的核心。声名赫赫如《水舞间》，至今仍未收回成本。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这也是澳门的难题。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">那些令人迷醉的建筑、奢华的内设，都建立在赌博高额的利润基础之上。转型，是拿“发动机开刀”；不转型，单一的产业寄生模式，高达35%的行业税负，随时都可能倾塌于外部的高压之下。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/16.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">新濠影汇内景</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">率先转型、先吃螃蟹，是美味还是毒药？暂未可知。在大多数竞争对手选择观望之际，何猷龙押上了32亿美元。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">会有压力吗？他坦言“不仅有，而且压力很大”。如果澳门经济势头不能止跌，32亿美元的“学费”足以将他此前的成就横扫一空。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“但是”，何猷龙话锋一转：“压力随时都有，以前，有一间摩卡（俱乐部），对我来说都是不可能的梦想。”</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="85713" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; width: 50px; border: none rgb(172, 29, 16); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibEH82vfP7Aa2wic3y5MwmI43yB9icJz1SnvZ9cg0G1vNVaGOUeSnLAWlQTrd99SURN3H8UGZFFCjeOA/0?wx_fmt=png); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); background-size: contain; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 40px !important; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">
       <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">9</span></strong></p>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“赌王只有一个”</span></strong></p>
     </section>
     <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="">这是外界将他评为“最像赌王的人”的原因之一：他和父亲很像，五官、才干，以及魄力。1969年，何鸿瞿6000万港币投建葡京娱乐场时，也有人断言他将赔得血本无归。</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/17.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
     <section data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">不过，在谈及“小赌王”这个称号时，何猷龙却说：“澳门的赌王只有一个，就是我爸爸。”“我和他不一样，爸爸很有名，很有魅力，高大，也英俊。”他补充说。</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他与何鸿鋈肥涤泻芏嗖煌，比如，他比父亲矮了大半头。再比如，何鸿鲂劬岚拿诺陌敫鍪兰屠铮留下了很多“风流故事”，何猷龙在这方面则无甚可言。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">赌王曾感慨：“我这一生，只要我喜欢的女人，没有追不到手的，不过我同样不懂得怎么甩掉她们。”何猷龙则没有如此“幸福的烦恼“，他14岁便认识了太太罗秀茵，“拍拖”9年后完婚，多年来，香港的狗仔队未曾在他身上收获任何绯闻。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br /></p>
    <section class="135editor" data-id="7170" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
     <fieldset data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; border: 0px; width: auto; clear: both; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <img src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/18.jpg" data-="" border="0" vspace="0" opacity="" mapurl="" title="" data-ratio="0.6673640167364017" data-w="478" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 118) 5px 3px 6px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 662px !important; visibility: visible !important;" />
     </fieldset>
    </section>
    <p><span style="">（从左至右）何猷龙、罗秀茵与不丹王子Dasho Sangay Wangchuk</span><br /></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">父亲是个神话，他更像一个“普通人”。他不似何鸿瞿前阒荒苎鐾，访谈开始和结束时，他两度起身握手，鞠躬的幅度接近直角。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">有礼貌的人总是很“讨喜”。更何况，按照流行界定，暖男、拼爹、刷脸、总裁……他似乎没有死角。</span></p>
    <p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">神话正在老去，澳门风云激荡。这个在政协会议上，会竖着耳朵做笔记的年轻人，能握住澳门下一轮经济的命脉吗？</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://img.zaoing.com/article/ypoq4vg6/19.jpg" data-ratio="0.4407114624505929" data-w="" /><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一键关注，即刻与澳中企业家互动！</span></strong></p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p> 
